dct_title_s: Kankoku kōutsū zenzu; Tōyō tetsudō oyobi kōro renrakuzu
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows various land and sea routes, waterways, anchorages, cities and towns.
